		For a full refund, cancellation must be made five full days before the event. For example, if the event is on Friday, cancel by the previous Sunday before. <br><br>

		<strong>Strict: 50% refund up until 1 week prior to event, except fees</strong><br><br>

		For a 50% refund, cancellation must be made seven full days prior to the event, otherwise no refund. For example, if the event is on Friday, cancel by Friday of the previous week.<br><br>

